# Add Path to Knowledge Base

Add a temporary path to the current session's knowledge base.

## Usage

```
/lsearch-add <path>
```

## Arguments

- `path` (required): Path to add (file or directory)

## Description

Adds a path that is only valid for the current Claude Code session. The path will not persist after the session ends.

## Your task

Add the provided path to the knowledge base using lsearch add-path.
